<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <div class="nav-logo"><span class="taxmate-animated">Tax Mate</span></div>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/">Home</a>
                <a href="/taxbot">TaxBot</a>
                <a href="/auth/logout">Logout</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="form-container">
        <h1>Start Your Tax Filing</h1>
        <p>Welcome, <%= user.name %>! Let's file your income tax return step by step.</p>
        
        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-step active">1. Profile</div>
            <div class="progress-step">2. Income</div>
            <div class="progress-step">3. Deductions</div>
            <div class="progress-step">4. Regime</div>
            <div class="progress-step">5. Review</div>
            <div class="progress-step">6. File</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Ready to begin?</h3>
            <p>We'll guide you through the complete process:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Verify your personal information</li>
                <li>Enter income details or upload Form-16</li>
                <li>Claim eligible deductions</li>
                <li>Compare tax regimes</li>
                <li>File your return securely</li>
            </ul>
            
            <a href="/filing/step1" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Start Filing Process</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>